---
source: src/highlighting/highlighter.rs
expression: "cfg.highlight(\"~/foo/a.sh && ~/foo/b.sh # comment\")?\n.to_string().replace(cfg.homedir.path().to_str().unwrap(), \"<HOME>\")"
---
~/foo/a.sh && ~/foo/b.sh # comment

0   10  `~/foo/a.sh`   CALLABLE `<HOME>/foo/a.sh`
11  13  `&&`           keyword.operator.logical.and
14  25  `~/foo/b.sh `  CALLABLE `<HOME>/foo/b.sh`
25  26  `#`            punctuation.definition.comment.begin
26  34  ` comment`     comment.line.number-sign
